Title: A Thousand Words Official Trailer #1 - Eddie Murphy Movie (2012) HD
Comment: When Eddie finally bowed in submission at the tree and prayed  not aloud but within his spirit there was a quietness. to me this was praying in the spirit as I've heard ministers preach about. I understand this because our mouth tongue is so vile why would God want to hear it. so it's the spirit within that He  hears. Then after that Eddie started showing love more by giving instead of saying it. Each time a leaf kept falling an he still felt he was going to die when the last leaf fell. I always figured he wasn't going to die because with each act of love he did it was renewing an love was there. love is healing. an he was feeling this within.  of course at the end the tree became fully bloomed of leaves brighter and more vibrant than before.  this seemed like to me the New Birth. Born again sermons I have heard so much of over the years  but was never received so vividly as this movie. This movie should be shown in churches so others who may not connect the meaning of praying in the spirit.& giving in love. whoever wrote this movie in ingenious.  it may just accomplish what some ministers have been trying to do for the longest.  It's a truly deep movie.
